snippet.title: Best VGM 1042 - Bastion - Setting Sail, Coming Home (End Theme)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Xbox 360
Bastion (2011)
Setting Sail, Coming Home (End Theme)
Darren Korb
